{"tid":451692,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【泰國退休】金融人舉家移居芭堤雅 執葉炒股過日辰","createTime":"2017-10-29T12:59:24.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-29T18:19:17.000Z","uid":62551,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"16df1faf84da5a36d149565a48958c5833a5b275","tid":451692,"uid":62551,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-29T12:59:24.000Z","msg":"公平咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/realtime/article/20171028/57381039\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20171028%2F57381039&d=XwQlyROJB9lzKPRASNs25tr9upuAghWR75VkZoMWgf8%3D&h=7fa0ebaa\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20171028%2F57381039&h=53fe262a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/realtime/article/20171028/57381039</a><br />\n<br />\n今日的香港，政治混亂不再話下，更不知不覺間變成了一個月薪十萬都買不起樓，到茶餐廳吃個飯都要五、六十蚊才能落樓的陌生地方，離開似乎成了港人自救的出路。港人熱門旅遊地點泰國，空間大、物價低，近年很多人視她為理想的退休勝地，香港的「無殼蝸牛」亦紛紛轉戰當地買樓，一圓上車夢。今次我們就走到泰國，尋找一群移居泰國的香港人，細聽他們逃走他鄉的故事。<br />\n<br />\n現在56歲的施昌勤（Aaron），原本在香港從事金融，曾在J.P. Morgan任職，擁有高薪厚職，太太是全職主婦，兒子讀國際學校，家住貝澳三層村屋，有車有樓，是典型的中產家庭。三年多前退休後，錢要慳住使，當時正值佔中，眼見香港政治環境惡劣，加上大量強國人湧港，環境逐漸污染，為了健康和將來，萌生出走念頭，決定申請泰國退休簽證，並賣掉香港的資產，2015年10月帶同太太馮錦芳（Winnie）和兒子逃出香港，移居到泰國芭堤雅，開展新生活。"},{"pid":"52ab7a1ed17c5fc92dbf3a1005374a3e8f3217c2","tid":451692,"uid":30169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-29T13:09:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6efc8e5d2ac233d5469360a7bcf413abfac5a31d","tid":451692,"uid":58862,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-29T13:16:03.000Z","msg":"關我撚事咩<br />\n咁都放上連登"},{"pid":"bb63dcb14e616bea9daff2c1ffa636d6c975421f","tid":451692,"uid":10692,"like"